  <abstract>Recto annotation: Columbia memorial Church, Colony, Ok  Dr. Roe Says" Do not tie yourself up to a Foreign Mission Val. Pledge as the Lord may want you for Home Indians</abstract>
  <abstract>Verso annotation: Dear E. Glad to think of you all gathering in the Name of Christ . Our Henry is in the Yale Del. Address c/o Fuller, 3-44 East Ave There will also be [acceptance?]of our Indian workers who may be a comrade of yours next semester Mr Jas. Bell. Louisville Theo. Seminary, Ky.  Henry can tell you where he is. M W. Roe </abstract>
